6,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f58121cfec4e8d53c0255dbc119be2c6eca74922","tid":1656790,"uid":209225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:09:09.000Z","msg":"打好關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n同同事打好關係<br />\n傾多D計，言語之間佢地會教你好多野<br />\n熟絡左，有咩事佢地都會幫你<br />\n時間耐左，你搵到自己係公司既定位，返工就會輕鬆d"},{"pid":"76b1ae1a10e01fb592195147ac0240314be06bc0","tid":1656790,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T19:16:02.000Z","msg":"求幫推 p牌仔推唔喐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【簡易文宣】本土國際戰線&mdash;Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656652</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"54bbddfcdbc107b7a0cc79ba2818ea7d1b3cdf11","tid":1656790,"uid":126731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T21:39:51.000Z","msg":"轉工。鳩鬧既人唔會收皮。一係屌到佢反皮。夠惡就食得返佢。"},{"pid":"e48b8ddfa98eb188931485ea2f3d06b03fc781ef","tid":1656790,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T21:45:46.000Z","msg":"訓多啲 翻工醒少少 唔識就努力學多啲 唔好成日比人拋到"},{"pid":"e4c1b1ad3050c66f0187ec90a704c55c5101e022","tid":1656790,"uid":27416,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T21:51:32.000Z","msg":"方向錯誤<br />\n應該係問點先可以唔介意被人鬧"},{"pid":"ee4c74070b8207327360b7eeb069e15a0b2a74bc","tid":1656790,"uid":185565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T21:59:07.000Z","msg":"冷靜處理便可 <br />\n搵方法去記一啲成日忘記既日常程序（eg.抄落嚟提醒自己）<br />\n唔識就問 得出答案可重複第二點以免忘記<br />\n不過做好公關 就會順風順水好多 <br />\n另外新接觸既事多啲做rehearsal<br />\n其實你做錯因為唔熟姐"},{"pid":"cacc2586512a22e80739e7ceeb87ac4c4c9744a4","tid":1656790,"uid":14337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:06:39.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"0a63e73182932509fc486f38f782e3375698abc5","tid":1656790,"uid":4256,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:12:24.000Z","msg":"唔好care 做錯野係正常<br />\n有d老屎忽心地差就會針住你黎屌<br />\n你可以當佢地發嗡風"},{"pid":"83cada952f6f90024a950d69f3aa5d32d2c44589","tid":1656790,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:24:57.000Z","msg":"搵份好工<br />\n同事返工無壓力自然客氣d<br />\n例如公務員（非紀律部隊）"},{"pid":"08c75b431e5ca78a22208cb6993df7984db42638","tid":1656790,"uid":202898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:28:07.000Z","msg":"話完都唔好改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老屎忽心態<br />\n之後d人就懶得話你了"},{"pid":"bf85a96aa8fdc1fd915d01fc21c80f42a9005a63","tid":1656790,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"姣溝老世"},{"pid":"6cb137c5cced31dca9f1d5b36d5690f226c6343e","tid":1656790,"uid":52264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"421308329066bd5f16c843996247e220096e6249","tid":1656790,"uid":70291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"新仔<br />\n實比人蝦，睇下自己大佬係咩料，大佬同其他人關係好唔好同做唔做到野好影響同事對你。<br />\n準備一本薄仔，人地同你講乜都寫落去，一來防止自己唔記得，二來可以比人見到你有重視佢講野。<br />\n做野慢慢做，重要野自己對過先正式交比人。<br />\n唔好試新方法，同事用咩方法你就照跟，如果唔係佢地唔識得同你執屎如果你做錯左。"},{"pid":"f85ea9ff71c9540745d4e8ca1ff685951e71d308","tid":1656790,"uid":12302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"醒少少 唔使比人屌"},{"pid":"f9624a7b61ca3619c7e7f00435c516a4d9c04027","tid":1656790,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:46:13.000Z","msg":"一係諗方法埋堆 佢當你係自己人就得 唔得就轉工 無謂勉強"},{"pid":"035fdfaf6b674f5dc9bad282f38fccc844ebdd32","tid":1656790,"uid":127528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:49:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d3133372f84a6fe74e57f20c217a5bd81c05806","tid":1656790,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"fresh grad??"},{"pid":"fb4ab75205b3769d0ba753552424a5017b868c32","t